data.description: Upgraded and well maintained townhome is ready for you. Boasting a spacious floor plan, this home is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying cozy family nights. Spacious 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Giving open-concept living and dining area with abundant natural light. Master suite retreat with ensuite bathroom and custom built walk-in closet. Inviting deck within a private fenced back yard. Both convenience and comfort, this home is situated minutes from downtown Decatur. Come see for yourself!
